| location = Weinheim
| doi = 10.1002/14356007.a11_141
| isbn = 3-527-30673-0 }}</ref>

==应用==
二苯醚主要用于与[[联苯|联苯]]混合形成低共熔物，由于混合物处于液态的温度区间非常大，故适宜用作[[热传递|热传递]]介质。

二苯醚是通过Ferrario反应生产[[吩噁噻|吩噁噻]]的起始原料，<ref>{{OrgSynth
| author = Suter, C. M.; Maxwell, C. E.
| title =  Phenoxthin
| journal = Organic Syntheses
| collvol =  2
| issue =  
| collvolpages = 485
| year =  1943
| prep = cv2p0485}}</ref>后者用于[[聚酰胺|聚酰胺]]和[[聚酰亚胺|聚酰亚胺]]的生产。<ref>{{cite journal
| author = Mitsuru Ueoda, Tatsuo Aizawa, Yoshio Imai
| title =  Preparation and properties of polyamides and polyimides containing phenoxathiin units
| journal = Journal of Polymer Science: Polymer Chemistry Edition
| volume =  15
| issue =  11
| pages = 2739–2747
| year =  1977
| publisher = 
| location = 
| doi =10.1002/pol.1977.170151119 }}</ref>

由于其类似[[天竺葵|天竺葵]]的香味和其稳定性与廉价，二苯醚广泛用于肥皂的香味添加剂。<ref>{{OrgSynth
| author = Ungnade, H. E.; Orwoll, E. F.
| title =  2-Methoxy Diphenyl Ether
| collvol =  3
| collvolpages = 566
| year =  1955
| prep = cv3p0566}}</ref>二苯醚也作为生产[[聚酯|聚酯]]的加工助剂。

{{en-link|多溴代二苯醚|Polybrominated diphenyl ethers|多溴代二苯醚}}（PBDE）用于[[阻燃剂_(塑胶)|阻燃剂]]，五溴代与八溴代二苯醚由于健康与环境方面的风险，于2003年被欧盟禁止使用，<ref name="EU-Ban">{{Cite web |url=http://eur-lex.europa.eu/LexUriServ/site/en/oj/2003/l_042/l_04220030215en00450046.pdf |title=DIRECTIVE 2003/11/EC of the European Parliament and of the Council |accessdate=2013-08-28 |archive-date=2013-05-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130525173756/http://eur-lex.europa.eu/LexUriServ/site/en/oj/2003/l_042/l_04220030215en00450046.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>现只有十溴二苯醚仍广泛使用，<ref>{{cite journal
| author = Sutker, B. J.
| title =  Flame Retardants
| journal = Ullmann's Encyclopedia of Industrial Chemistry
| volume =  
| issue =  
| pages = 
| year =  2005
| publisher = Wiley-VCH
| location = Weinheim
| doi = 10.1002/14356007.a11_123
| isbn = 3-527-30673-0 }}</ref>涂料和纤维增强塑料的制造中十溴二苯醚以阻燃剂102为商品名出售。

